FuncDef:
The access-filter command displays the iNOF host access interface whitelist view.
The undo access-filter command deletes the iNOF host access interface whitelist view and all configurations in the view. The access-filter command displays the iNOF host access interface whitelist view. The undo access-filter command deletes the iNOF host access interface whitelist view and all configurations in the view. By default, the iNOF host access interface whitelist view is not created. This command is supported only on the CE6860-SAN, CE6866K, CE6866, CE6860-HAM, CE6885-SAN, CE8850-SAN, CE8851K, CE8851-32CQ8DQ-P and CE8850-HAM.
